# Text Generation

## About the Project
In this project, I built a simple text generation model that generates new text based on given input data.

## What I Did
- Used a sample text dataset
- Created a mapping of words based on their sequence
- Generated new text using pattern-based learning

## Result
The model was able to generate meaningful text sequences based on learned patterns.

## Conclusion
This project helped me understand how text generation works and how machines can learn patterns from text data.